Product Backlog:
User Authentication and Security:

As a user, I want to log in securely using multi-factor authentication (MFA).
As a user, I want to reset my password via email verification.
As a user, I want role-based access control (RBAC) to restrict access to certain features based on user roles.
As a system administrator, I want to audit user activity and track login attempts for security purposes.
Population Reporting:

As a user, I want to generate reports for specific time periods (e.g., annual, quarterly) to analyze population trends over time.
As a user, I want to filter population reports based on demographic factors such as age, gender, and ethnicity.
As a user, I want to export population reports in various formats (e.g., CSV, PDF) for further analysis or sharing.
As a user, I want to schedule automated population reports to be generated and emailed to stakeholders at regular intervals.
City Reporting:

As a user, I want to visualize city populations on an interactive map for better geographical understanding.
As a user, I want to drill down into city reports to view detailed demographic information such as median age, income distribution, and education level.
As a user, I want to compare city populations across different time periods to identify growth patterns and trends.
As a user, I want to receive alerts when a city's population exceeds a certain threshold or when significant demographic changes occur.
Capital City Reporting:

As a user, I want to analyze the relationship between capital city populations and key socio-economic indicators (e.g., GDP per capita, employment rate).
As a user, I want to forecast future population growth for capital cities using predictive analytics models.
As a user, I want to generate heatmaps to visualize population density and distribution within capital cities.
Language Statistics:

As a user, I want to track language proficiency levels and language education programs to understand language adoption trends.
As a user, I want to analyze language diversity and linguistic minorities within different regions and countries.
As a user, I want to identify correlations between language spoken and economic indicators such as tourism revenue and international trade.
Population Distribution Reporting:

As a user, I want to analyze migration patterns and population movements between different regions and countries.
As a user, I want to assess the impact of urbanization on population distribution and city growth rates.
As a user, I want to conduct spatial analysis to identify areas with high population density and potential infrastructure needs.
Additional Functionality:

As a user, I want the system to integrate with external data sources (e.g., census data, social media APIs) for enriched population analysis.
As a user, I want to collaborate with team members by sharing and annotating population reports in real-time.
As a user, I want to receive personalized recommendations and insights based on population data analysis and machine learning algorithms.
As a user, I want to perform advanced statistical analysis and hypothesis testing to uncover hidden patterns and relationships within the population data
